<headline>Special Weather Statement issued June 08 at 4:22AM EDT  by NWS Cleveland</headline>
<description>...Areas of fog early this morning...
Areas of fog will continue through sunrise across Northeast Ohio
and Northwest Pennsylvania. Visibilities are fluctuating and will
occasionally drop to a quarter mile or less, especially in
valleys and low lying areas. Motorists should use caution and be
prepared to slow down if they encounter fog.</description>
